Additionally, the Copyright Policy from GraceToYou (gty.org) must be observed when using this software to download and distribute any material:

Grace to You is the official repository of all of John MacArthur’s Bible-teaching material. We want to maximize your flexibility in sharing resources while simultaneously maintaining quality control and connecting people with our ministry. Please partner with us by observing the following guidelines.

Online Distribution
You may link to and share media produced by Grace to You, but you may not post that media on your website or host them on your media channel. You may not create or use edited versions of Grace to You media without permission.

Offline Distribution
You may duplicate and distribute John’s audio and video messages in CD, DVD, and digital formats without prior permission as long as you follow the restrictions outlined below.

    You may duplicate and distribute only full-length versions of the messages.
    You may not edit the content in any way.
    You may not charge for the material (even to recoup your costs).
    If you copy material to a CD or DVD, please include the following information on the CD or DVD:
        The title of the message
        “Copyright [fill in the year of the message] by John MacArthur. Used by permission from Grace to You.”
        gty.org
        800-55-GRACE
    You may not include personal or organizational contact information on any CDs or DVDs.
    You may not use or reproduce the Grace to You logo for any purpose, with the exception that the Grace to You logo may appear on your website as a clickable link that redirects the user to the Grace to You website.
    The rebranding of Grace to You materials is prohibited.  No logo, graphic embellishment, word or words, mark of any kind, audio recording, or video recording may be added to any Grace to You audio resource or video resource.

Grace to You and John MacArthur reserve all copyright protections under applicable law and we reserve the right to revoke or modify these permissions at any time. 